data.description: Come and see this beautiful home located in the heart of Jacksonville! This home has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. The kitchen seamlessly transitions into the formal dining room, creating an inviting space for gatherings. The open living room enhances the sense of spaciousness and warmth throughout the home.Step outside to a large-sized deck, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying outdoor leisure. The deck overlooks a stunning in-ground pool, creating an oasis of relaxation and entertainment in your own backyard.Schedule your appointment today and envision the possibilities of making this house your dream home!
